ired%20faux%20wooden%20handle).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20we've%20used%20this%20Hisense%20refrigerator%20every%20day%20for%20about%20half%20a%20year%2C%20I've%20pulled%20together%20our%20impressions%20of%20the%20brand's%20fridges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EDimensions%20and%20design%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221610%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22diagram%20of%20a%20hisense%20refrigerator%20including%20dimensions%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e0a10c8855cc2458f718176%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221022%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHisense%2FLowes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHisense%20makes%20several%20bottom-freezer%20fridge%20models.%20I%20tested%20the%20%3Ca%20data-xid%3D%5C%22fr1626979925334dfe%5C%22%20data-ml%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20data-orig-url%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freviews%2Fout%3Fplatform%3Dbrowser%26amp%3BpostSource%3Dbi%257C5e0a0953855cc242010da7f4%26amp%3Bsc%3Dfalse%26amp%3Bsessionid%3D16269799213753cc6rf9p%26amp%3Btype%3DALREADY-AFFILIATE-LINK-NOT-AMAZON%26amp%3Bu%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fgo.redirectingat.com%252F%253Fid%253D35871X943606%2526xcust%253Dbiip_011520_hisense-refrigerator-review%2526url%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.lowes.com%25252Fpd%25252FHisense-17-1-cu-ft-Bottom-Freezer-Refrigerator-Stainless-Steel-ENERGY-STAR%25252F1001105742%26amp%3Bxcust%3D1626979922036arhe85ve7%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20nofollow%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20data-ml-id%3D%5C%223%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%2212bf09cbbc30db3a15c9d5a4b6059feb%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22summary_bullets%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-11409-20%26h%3D7afd9e14e32b28c1bf1d6a115b00680503fa974baccea805cdd5fac3d49fef38%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42b12%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fhisense-bottom-freezer-refrigerator-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.lowes.com%252Fpd%252FHisense-17-1-cu-ft-Counter-depth-Bottom-Freezer-Refrigerator-Stainless-Steel-ENERGY-STAR%252F1001105742%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E17.1%20cubic-foot%20Bottom-Freezer%20Refrigerator%20(HBM17158SS)%3C%2Fa%3E%20model%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20out%20of%20stock.%20However%2C%20you%20can%20find%20slightly%20larger%2017.2%20cubic-foot%20models%20available%20in%20the%20same%20design.%20Here%20are%20the%20specs%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-11409-20%26h%3Dfb4a5f93940db6f4997a711cc6f925c3c5e319f6306d95226306af349f2acf35%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42b12%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fhisense-bottom-freezer-refrigerator-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.lowes.com%252Fpd%252FHisense-17-2-cu-ft-Bottom-Freezer-Refrigerator-Stainless-steel-ENERGY-STAR%252F5001252387%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHRB171N6ASE%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0model.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeight%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2069.1%20inches%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDepth%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2029.1%20inches%20with%20handles%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWidth%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2031.1%20inches%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETotal%20capacity%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E17.2%20cubic%20feet%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFridge%20capacity%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2012.1%20cubic%20feet%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFreezer%20capacity%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%205.1%20cubic%20feet%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnergy%20Star%20certified%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fpdf.lowes.com%2Fenergyguides%2F819130025995.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYes%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWarranty%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%202%20years%20parts%20and%20labor%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20freezer%20is%20located%20at%20the%20bottom%20instead%20of%20the%20top.%20If%20you%20primarily%20use%20fresh%20foods%20and%20don't%20look%20in%20your%20freezer%20too%20often%2C%20this%20is%20an%20ideal%20setup%2C%20as%20the%20foods%20you%20use%20most%20frequently%20are%20located%20right%20at%20eye%20level%20and%20easily%20in%20reach.%20The%20freezer%20has%20two%20compartments%20so%20you%20can%20store%20larger%20items%20in%20the%20bottom%20drawer%20and%20smaller%20ones%20in%20the%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fridge%20is%20tall%20at%20about%2070%20inches%20in%20height%20and%20slim%20at%2031-inches%20wide%2C%20so%20it%20can%20fit%20in%20small%20kitchens.%20It%20requires%20just%2033%20inches%20of%20space%20to%20fit%20through%20a%20doorway%20for%20installation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20door%20is%20reversible%2C%20meaning%20you%20can%20install%20it%20so%20that%20it%20opens%20to%20the%20left%20instead%20of%20the%20right%20if%20need%20be.%20You%20will%20need%20a%20Philips%20screwdriver%20and%20an%208-millimeter%20socket%20wrench%20to%20do%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ESetup%20process%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22interior%20of%20hisense%20refrigerator%20include%20door%20with%20storage%20shelves%2C%20produce%20drawer%2C%20and%20main%20shelf%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e0a4ebd855cc27670368032%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMalarie%20Gokey%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGetting%20a%20new%20fridge%20into%20a%20small%20New%20York%20City%20apartment%20is%20never%20easy%2C%20but%20the%20process%20went%20as%20smoothly%20as%20can%20be%20expected.%20Our%20building's%20maintenance%20man%20helped%20us%20bring%20the%20fridge%20up%20to%20the%20sixth%20floor%20in%20the%20elevator%20on%20a%20large%20dolly%20cart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20chose%20this%20fridge%20in%20part%20because%20it%20is%20actually%20slim%20enough%20to%20fit%20through%20the%20elevator%20door%2C%20the%20entrance%20to%20our%20apartment%2C%20and%20the%20kitchen%20doorway.%20Most%20fridges%20are%20simply%20too%20big%2C%20but%20this%20one%20fit%20in%20the%20elevator%20and%20our%20apartment's%20main%20entrance%20easily%20with%20a%20few%20inches%20to%20spare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20couldn't%20get%20it%20through%20the%20kitchen%20doorway%20while%20it%20was%20still%20in%20the%20box%2C%20so%20we%20cut%20the%20box%20open%20in%20sections%20with%20a%20box%20cutter%20until%20it%20was%20free.%20We%20removed%20the%20protective%20Styrofoam%20and%20plastic%20wrap%20to%20start%20wiggling%20it%20through%20the%20doorway%20inch%20by%20inch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20we%20moved%20the%20fridge%20slowly%20off%20the%20Styrofoam%20and%20plastic%20base%20to%20free%20the%20wheels%20up.%20Once%20that%20was%20done%2C%20we%20rolled%20it%20into%20place%20and%20plugged%20it%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%20up%3A%20handle%20installation.%20We%20found%20the%20handles%20safe%20inside%20the%20fridge%2C%20read%20the%20instructions%2C%20and%20broke%20out%20the%20included%20Allen%20wrench%20to%20start%20installing%20the%20handles.%20It%20was%20very%20easy%20to%20do%3A%20We%20lined%20up%20the%20handles%20with%20the%20screws%20on%20the%20front%20of%20the%20fridge%2C%20located%20the%20hole%20in%20the%20handle%2C%20and%20inserted%20the%20Allen%20wrench%20to%20tighten%20the%20screw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20twists%20of%20the%20wrench%20later%2C%20and%20the%20handles%20were%20attached.%20If%20you%20need%20the%20door%20to%20open%20in%20the%20opposite%20direction%2C%20you%20can%20switch%20it%20using%20the%20included%20kit%20and%20the%20instructions.%20We%20did%20not%20need%20to%20switch%20it%2C%20so%20we%20didn't%20try%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20removed%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20protective%20plastic%20on%20the%20fridge%20and%20the%20tape%20they%20used%20inside%20to%20secure%20the%20drawers%20and%20shelves%2C%20and%20finally%2C%20the%20fridge%20was%20ready%20to%20fill%20up%20with%20food.%20The%20entire%20set-up%20process%20only%20took%20half%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EInside%20the%20fridge%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hisense%20refrigerator%20loaded%20with%20bottles%20and%20jars%20of%20food%20and%20condiments%20on%20shelves%20and%20door%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e0a4f41855cc276f1339769%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMalarie%20Gokey%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fridge%20has%20three%20adjustable%20glass%20shelves%20inside%20and%20six%20heavy-duty%20plastic%20shelves%20in%20the%20door.%20You%20can%20move%20them%20around%20to%20suit%20your%20needs%2C%20though%20you%20are%20somewhat%20limited%20in%20the%20adjustments%20you%20can%20make%2C%20because%20of%20the%20grooves%20you%20need%20to%20slot%20the%20shelves%20into%20for%20stability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20spacious%20crisper%20drawer%20with%20two%20sections%20where%20you%20can%20house%20your%20fruits%20and%20vegetables.%20You%20can%20adjust%20the%20humidity%20of%20the%20drawer%20with%20a%20simple%20slider%20that%20opens%20or%20closes%20holes.%20You%20do%20have%20to%20pull%20the%20whole%20drawer%20out%20to%20access%20what's%20inside%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20opening%20one%20drawer%2C%20and%20that%20means%20you'll%20need%20the%20fridge%20door%20open%20wide%20enough%20to%20pull%20out%20the%20drawer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fridge%20has%20a%2012.1-cubic-foot%20capacity%2C%20which%20is%20a%20big%20upgrade%20over%20our%20previous%20small%20and%20ancient%20fridge.%20We%20were%20able%20to%20put%20a%201.53-liter%20Tropicana%20orange%20juice%20bottle%20and%20a%201-liter%20bottle%20of%20Coca-Cola%20in%20the%20bottom%20shelf%20of%20the%20door.%20In%20our%20old%20fridge%2C%20that%20simply%20wasn't%20possible%2C%20so%20we%20always%20had%20to%20squeeze%20tall%20bottles%20into%20awkward%20spaces%20or%20make%20them%20lie%20down%20and%20risk%20a%20spill.%20You%20can%20also%20fit%20a%20bottle%20of%20wine%20or%20Champagne%20in%20there%20for%20chilling%20upright%2C%20which%20we%20did%20for%20New%20Year's%20Eve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221599%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hisense%20Fridge%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e0a58bc855cc278080a5a44%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221199%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGuillermo%20Garzon%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20numerous%20shelves%20in%20the%20door%20also%20make%20it%20easy%20to%20store%20smaller%20items%20like%20sauces%20as%20well%20as%20eggs%20and%20butter%20so%20you%20can%20save%20space%20for%20larger%20foods%20inside%20on%20the%20three%20big%20glass%20shelves.%20We%20put%20our%20many%20different%20sauces%20and%20jams%20on%20the%20door%20shelves%2C%20and%20it%20has%20been%20a%20revelation.%20We%20can%20finally%20find%20the%20hoisin%20sauce%20without%20having%20to%20move%20things%20around%20frantically%20while%20the%20tofu%20burns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20negatives%2C%20we%20found%20that%20you%20can%20only%20fit%20a%20full%20gallon%20of%20milk%20in%20the%20fridge%20if%20you%20remove%20one%20of%20the%20interior%20glass%20shelves%20entirely%20and%20make%20do%20with%20two%20shelves%20instead%20of%20three.%20We%20ended%20up%20deciding%20to%20buy%20half%20gallons%20from%20now%20on%20instead%20of%20losing%20the%20extra%20space%20created%20by%20having%20all%20three%20shelves%20in%20place.%20However%2C%20if%20your%20family%20regularly%20buys%20gallons%20of%20milk%20%E2%80%94%20and%20many%20do!%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20important%20to%20note.%20Everything%20else%20fits%20in%20place%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20set%20the%20fridge%20temperature%20using%20the%20control%20panel%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20fridge's%20interior.%20Hisense%20recommends%20the%20pre-set%2039-degree%20temperature%20for%20the%20best%20results%2C%20so%20we%20left%20it%20at%20that%20at%20first.%20After%20a%20few%20months%2C%20we%20found%20that%20it%20was%20a%20bit%20too%20cold%2C%20so%20we%20adjusted%20the%20temperature%20to%2042%20degrees%20Fahrenheit.%20Changing%20the%20temperature%20was%20easy%3A%20I%20pressed%20down%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BFridge%26quot%3B%20button%20on%20the%20control%20panel%20for%20three%20seconds%20until%20it%20beeped%20and%20then%20kept%20pressing%20it%20to%20get%20to%20the%20temperature%20I%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inside%20of%20the%20fridge%20is%20illuminated%20by%20energy-saving%20LED%20lights%2C%20which%20is%20common%20on%20new%20fridges%2C%20but%20nonetheless%20exciting%20for%20anyone%20who's%20coming%20from%20an%20old%20fridge%20with%20a%20fragile%20bulb%20that%20needed%20replacing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EInside%20the%20freezer%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221599%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hisense%20Fridge%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e0a5776855cc27db65a4d75%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221199%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGuillermo%20Garzon%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20freezer%20is%20located%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20fridge%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20easy%20to%20access.%20When%20you%20pull%20the%20handle%2C%20the%20freezer%20opens%20smoothly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20a%205.1-cubic-foot%20capacity%20and%20two%20compartments%3A%20a%20top-level%20drawer%20that%20pulls%20out%20and%20a%20deeper%20bottom%20level%20compartment.%20We%20put%20all%20our%20most%20frequently%20used%20frozen%20items%2C%20ice%20cube%20trays%2C%20and%20smaller%20foods%20in%20the%20top%20drawer%20for%20easy%20access%20and%20saved%20the%20bottom%20compartment%20for%20bigger%20items%20(in%20our%20case%2C%20a%20giant%20bag%20of%20frozen%20peas%20and%20a%20stash%20of%20smoked%20salmon).%20It's%20important%20not%20to%20overload%20the%20top%20drawer%20with%20heavy%20items%2C%20because%20it%20can%20get%20off%20the%20drawer%20pull-out%20tracks%20when%20overloaded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHisense%20recommends%20the%20pre-set%20temperature%20of%20-2%20degrees%20for%20best%20results.%20Just%20like%20the%20fridge%20temperature%2C%20the%20freezer%20is%20easy%20to%20set.%20You%20simply%20press%20down%20the%20%26quot%3BFreezer%26quot%3B%20button%20in%20the%20fridge's%20control%20panel%20for%20three%20seconds%20until%20you%20hear%20a%20beep%2C%20and%20then%20keep%20pressing%20it%20to%20cycle%20through%20the%20different%20temperature%20settings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20found%20that%20temperature%20to%20be%20more%20than%20cold%20enough.%20We%20put%20a%20new%20bottle%20of%20Coca-Cola%20in%20there%20to%20chill%20before%20dinner%2C%20and%20within%20the%2020%20minutes%20we%20spent%20cooking%20dinner%2C%20it%20was%20icy%20cold%20and%20even%20partially%20frozen.%20In%20our%20old%20fridge%2C%20it%20wouldn't%20even%20have%20been%20chilled%20in%20that%20amount%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20need%20things%20to%20freeze%20quickly%2C%20the%20freezer%20also%20has%20a%20super%20freeze%20function%20that%20drops%20the%20temperature%20down%20to%20-13%C2%B0F%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20minutes%20to%20rapidly%20freeze%20the%20food.%20Hisense%20says%20it%20also%20helps%20the%20freezer%20maintain%20its%20-2%20temperature%20when%20you're%20adding%20a%20bunch%20of%20unfrozen%20(or%20partially%20unfrozen)%20items%20to%20the%20freezer%20at%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EIn%20daily%20use%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221599%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22full%20shot%20of%20interior%20of%20hisense%20refrigerator%20showing%20lots%20of%20storage%20for%20food%2C%20beverages%20and%20other%20food%20including%20produce%20like%20tomatoes%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e0a5311855cc273f06266a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221199%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGuillermo%20Garzon%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20about%20six%20months%20of%20daily%20use%2C%20I%20can%20confidently%20say%20this%20fridge%20has%20made%20our%20lives%20better.%20We%20cook%20a%20lot%2C%20so%20having%20a%20fridge%20that%20not%20only%20stores%20all%20the%20different%20foods%2C%20sauces%2C%20and%20drinks%20we%20like%20to%20have%20on%20hand%2C%20but%20also%20keeps%20it%20all%20organized%20makes%20preparing%20meals%20so%20much%20easier.%20When%20you%20can%20find%20what%20you're%20looking%20for%20in%20seconds%20instead%20of%20minutes%2C%20you%20don't%20ruin%20your%20meal%20or%20your%20mood.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20many%20different%20shelves%20in%20the%20fridge%20door%20made%20it%20super%20easy%20for%20us%20to%20organize%20all%20our%20sauces%20and%20keep%20small%20containers%20off%20the%20large%20main%20shelves.%20Now%20we%20can%20use%20all%20the%20space%20for%20larger%20foods%20and%20actually%20see%20all%20the%20food%20we%20have.%20Our%20drinks%20are%20also%20much%20cooler%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20think%20I%20realized%20just%20how%20badly%20our%20old%20fridge%20was%20working%20until%20I%20had%20a%20point%20of%20comparison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20love%20having%20the%20freezer%20at%20the%20bottom.%20It%20is%20so%20much%20easier%20to%20find%20things%20in%20the%20fridge%20when%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20bend%20over%2C%20kneel%20down%2C%20or%20as%20I%20often%20did%2C%20sit%20on%20the%20floor%20while%20rummaging%20around%20in%20the%20crisper%20drawers%20looking%20for%20the%20garlic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20you%20buy%20it%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EYes%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20have%20a%20small%20kitchen%20or%20you%20simply%20prefer%20a%20smaller%20fridge%2C%20it's%20a%20great%20choice%2C%20thanks%20to%20its%20spacious%20interior.%20It's%20also%20a%20good%20option%20for%20anyone%20who%20wants%20a%20fridge%20with%20the%20freezer%20at%20the%20bottom.%20It%20is%20reasonably%20priced%20when%20compared%20to%20fridges%20with%20a%20similar%20capacity%2C%20and%20it%20is%20one%20of%20the%20only%20bottom-freezer%20fridges%20with%20a%20similar%20capacity%20that%20you%20can%20buy%20for%20less%20than%20%241%2C000.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThere%20are%20so%20many%20fridges%20to%20choose%20from%2C%20so%20you%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20alternatives.%20You%20can%20check%20out%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-refrigerator%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20fridges%20under%20%242%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E.%20At%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-11409-20%26h%3Dfd20959fb9896e939c0b299d69573009cbcdbd8a5e40d7f1c07eb002e44776c0%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42b12%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fhisense-bottom-freezer-refrigerator-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.homedepot.com%252Fb%252FAppliances-Refrigerators-Bottom-Freezer-Refrigerators%252F16-18%252FN-5yc1vZc3p6Z1z19vsb%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Home%20Depot%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Lowe's%2C%20there%20are%20no%20bottom-freezer%20fridges%20with%20a%20similar%20capacity%20for%20less%20than%20%241%2C000%20(at%20the%20time%20of%20writing).%20You%20can%20find%20several%20fridges%20with%20a%20freezer%20at%20the%20top%20and%20a%20similar%20capacity%20for%20a%20bit%20less%20%E2%80%94%20prices%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-11409-20%26h%3Dfd20959fb9896e939c0b299d69573009cbcdbd8a5e40d7f1c07eb002e44776