ugh%20there%20is%20the%20option%20of%20buying%20new%2C%20what%20are%20you%20supposed%20to%20do%20with%20the%20old%20furniture%3F%20I%20know%20enough%20people%20who%20would%20rather%20sleep%20on%20a%20broken%20bed%20than%20carry%20a%20new%20one%20up%20five%20flights%20of%20stairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20a%20little%20research%20and%20personal%20experience%2C%20I%20found%20a%20dozen%20ways%20to%20completely%20refurbish%20old%20furniture.%20The%20best%20part%20about%20all%20these%20projects%20is%20that%20they're%20all%20pretty%20simple%20to%20carry%20out%20and%20they%20all%20cost%20way%20less%20than%20investing%20in%20a%20brand%20new%20piece.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EThese%2012%20products%20can%20help%20you%20refinish%20and%20refurbish%20old%20furniture%2C%20countertops%2C%20and%20more%3A%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOld%20English%20Scratch%20Cover%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221039%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Old%20English%20Scratch%20Cover%20for%20Wood%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c76b77126289837c627cac6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22779%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F2HbFM3N%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOld%20English%20Scratch%20Cover%20for%20Wood%2C%20%245.38%2C%20available%20at%20Amazon%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20should%20you%20use%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20scratch%20cover%20is%20an%20ideal%20solution%20to%20obnoxious%20surface-level%20scratches%20in%20dark-wood%20furniture.%20Though%20it%20does%20not%20fill%20indentations%2C%20it%20polishes%20wood%20and%20hides%20visible%20scratches%20by%20staining%20them%20to%20match%20your%20original%20piece.%20The%20formula%20is%20intended%20to%20be%20permanent%20to%20keep%20your%20furniture%20looking%20pristine%20for%20an%20extended%20period%20of%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cs