er.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-38580-20%26h%3D43e787686706a0f8d727c15e2ca17b3fe5f97b165ecf14e637aac591766946eb%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42897%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fperigold-luxury-furniture-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.anrdoezrs.net%252Flinks%252F6415797%252Ftype%252Fdlg%252Fsid%252Fbiipf_100419_perigold-luxury-furniture-review%252Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.perigold.com%252Fbrand%252Fbnd%252Fhooker-furniture-b1513.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Every%20highly-rated%20on%20Perigold%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20an%20average%20of%204.7%20stars%20our%205%20with%20more%20than%2027%2C000%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20table%20was%20similar%20to%20one%20of%20Restoration%20Hardware's%20most%20popular%20styles%20that%20I%20had%20my%20eye%20on%20for%20a%20while%2C%20but%20cost%20significantly%20less%20and%20featured%20unique%20design%20elements.%20The%20RH%20table%20alone%20costs%20over%20%247%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20almost%20%245%2C000%20more%20than%20this%20one.%20I%20also%20really%20liked%20the%20chairs%20that%20went%20along%20with%20the%20table%2C%20which%20were%20sold%20a%20la%20carte%20or%20as%20a%20complete%20set%20with%20the%20table.%20The%20complete%20set%2C%20including%20the%20table%20and%20eight%20chairs%2C%20cost%20less%20than%20the%20RH%20table%20alone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Perigold%20tables%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5d88c5e22e22af107322a688%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUnlike%20experiences%20I've%20had%20with%20other%20brands%2C%20the%20Hooker%20table%20looked%20even%20more%20beautiful%20in%20person%20than%20online.%3Cp%3EPerigold%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EOrder%20and%20delivery%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20whole%20experience%20with%20Perigold%2C%20from%20placing%20my%20order%20to%20delivery%2C%20was%20absolutely%20seamless.%20Less%20than%20a%20week%20after%20my%20order%20was%20placed%2C%20I%20received%20a%20call%20to%20schedule%20delivery%2C%20which%20was%20set%20up%20for%20a%20few%20days%20later.%20Some%20items%2C%20depending%20on%20their%20size%20and%20delivery%20type%2C%20can%20even%20be%20delivered%20in%20just%20a%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20delivery%20day%2C%20the%20drivers%20showed%20up%20promptly.%20My%20table%20and%20chairs%20arrived%20in%20several%2C%20huge%20boxes.%20I%20honestly%20don't%20know%20how%20I%20would%20have%20been%20able%20to%20unpack%20them%20and%20assemble%20the%20set%20myself.%20The%20drivers%20carefully%20unpacked%20and%20assembled%20every%20piece%2C%20taking%20away%20all%20of%20the%20boxes%20and%20packing%20material%20when%20they%20left.%20Altogether%2C%20they%20were%20at%20my%20home%20for%20about%20two%20hours%2C%20which%20was%20incredibly%20impressive%2C%20considering%20most%20furniture%20delivery%20people%20are%20in%20and%20out%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible.%20They%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20care%20into%20delivering%20and%20assembling%20my%20new%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20table%20itself%2C%20unlike%20experiences%20I've%20had%20with%20other%20furniture%20brands%2C%20it%20looked%20even%20more%20beautiful%20in%20person%20than%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Perigold%20furniture%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5d974fe6ec72bd0add55f6a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20table%20was%20similar%20to%20one%20of%20Restoration%20Hardware's%20most%20popular%20styles%20that%20I%20had%20my%20eye%20on%20for%20a%20while%2C%20but%20cost%20significantly%20less.%3Cp%3ELeah%20Groth%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EShipping%20and%20return%20policies%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomething%20else%20I%20was%20immediately%20drawn%20to%20was%20the%20free%2C%20all-inclusive%20delivery%20and%20assembly.%20Many%20other%20furniture%20companies%20and%20stores%20char