0per%20year.%20Is%20InHome%20worth%20the%20extra%20%2450%3F%20We'll%20explain%20everything%20you%20get%20for%20the%20price%20of%20Walmart%20InHome.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPrice%3Cp%3EWalmart%20InHome%20costs%20%2419.95%20a%20month%20or%20%24148%20per%20year.%20You%20can%20test%20it%20out%20with%20a%20free%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finhome.walmart.com%2Fget-started%2F%3Futm_source%3DMedia%26utm_medium%3DBusinessInsider1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E30-day%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat's%20included%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221332%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Walmart%20employee%20puts%20groceries%20away%20in%20a%20refrigerator%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Walmart%20InHome%20delivery%20service.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6238dc5e6197bc001876ba9a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22999%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20three%20main%20features%20to%20Walmart's%20InHome%20service%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finhome.walmart.com%2Fgrocery%3Futm_source%3DMedia%26utm_medium%3DBusinessInsider1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EInHome%20Grocery%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20Walmart%20employee%20will%20bring%20your%20groceries%20inside%20your%20home%20and%20put%20perishable%20items%20inside%20the%20refrigerator.%20Everything%20else%20is%20left%20wherever%20you%20prefer%3A%20on%20the%20counter%2C%20near%20the%20front%20door%2C%20in%20the%20garage%2C%20etc.%20Your%20order%20must%20be%20%2435%20or%20more%2C%20pre-tax%2C%20to%20qualify%20for%20in-home%20delivery%2C%20or%20there%20will%20be%20a%20%245.99%20service%20fee.%3C%2Fp