tations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EScan%20%26amp%3B%20go%2C%20which%20lets%20you%20use%20your%20phone%20to%20scan%20items%20as%20you%20shop%20then%20use%20a%20self-checkout%20station%20to%20pay.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERx%20for%20less%2C%20with%20up%20to%2085%25%20off%20for%20thousands%20of%20prescriptions%20at%20Walmart%20Pharmacies.%20Plus%2C%20there%20are%20six%20prescription%20medications%20that%20Walmart%2B%20members%20get%20for%20free%20in%20most%20states.%20You%20can%20read%20more%20about%20it%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fwalmart-plus-benefit-rx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20it%20works%3Cp%3EWalmart%20employees%20can%20enter%20your%20house%20or%20garage%20one%20of%20three%20ways%3A%20via%20an%20entry%20keypad%2C%20smart%20lock%2C%20or%20smart%20garage%20door%20opener.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20you%20can%20use%20any%20type%20of%20entry%20keypad%2C%20you'll%20have%20to%20store%20the%20code%20in%20the%20InHome%20app.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20locks%20and%20garage%20doors%2C%20the%20service%20requires%20specific%20smart-home%20gear.%20That%20includes%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-53763-20%26h%3D959720bd8ac433ca9082062576fe2e9dfdb7a580ba99e7b1c8fa84ff65842369%26postID%3D6238d8c3e1ca0a7cf26405d4%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fwalmart-inhome-price%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Flevel.co%252Fproducts%252Fbolt%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELevel%3C%2Fa%3E-brand%20lock%20for%20home%20entry%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finhome.walmart.com%2Ffyi%2Fgenie%3Futm_source%3DMedia%26utm_medium%3DBusinessInsider1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGenie%3C%2Fa%3E%20garage-door%20op