iscipline%20must%20go%20hand%20in%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-2_11zon-1757076501.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20foundation%20enforces%20a%20%E2%80%9CNo%20School%2C%20No%20Football%E2%80%9D%20rule%2C%20linking%20access%20to%20football%20training%20to%20consistent%20school%20attendance.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-2_11zon-1757076501.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-2_11zon-1757076501-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-2_11zon-1757076501-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-2_11zon-1757076501-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-2_11zon-1757076501-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-497017%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20foundation%20enforces%20a%20%E2%80%9CNo%20School%2C%20No%20Football%E2%80%9D%20rule%2C%20linking%20access%20to%20football%20training%20to%20consistent%20school%20attendance.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20many%20kids%20thought%20that%20if%20they%20were%20good%20at%20football%2C%20studies%20didn%E2%80%99t%20matter.%20But%20OSCAR%20showed%20us%20that%20school%20is%20our%20first%20priority%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20encouragement%2C%20Yamini%20never%20thought%20of%20dropping%20out.%20Still%2C%20relatives%20and%20neighbours%20often%20questioned%20her%20choices%3A%20%E2%80%9CShe%E2%80%99s%20a%20girl.%20What%20future%20does%2